fi.grimripper.loww.movement

Class DefaultMovement.PathData

  • java.lang.Object
    • fi.grimripper.loww.movement.DefaultMovement.PathData
  • Enclosing class:
    DefaultMovement

    protected static class DefaultMovement.PathData
extends java.lang.Object
    A data object to store movement data relevant to a single tile in a path. Paths can change by facing if template is asymmetric. The tiles occupied at the destination can also vary depending on facing.
    Author:
    Marko Tuominen

        totalCost - total cost needed to reach the tile
        minHeight - minimum height without terrain
        moveHeight - movement height at the tile
        facing - the mobile object's facing when moving through the tile
        templateFacing - facing for the mobile object's template in the tile
        risk - risk to reach the tile
